        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "&quot;Cash Prizes Scheme&quot; was launched by the Bihar Building &amp; Other Construction Workers Welfare Board (BBOCWWB), Labour Resources Department, Government of Bihar. Students securing 60% or more in the 10th and 12th exams receive cash prizes of up to ₹25,000/- per year. Upto two children of a registered construction worker are eligible.\n",
        "benefits_md": "\n- On securing 80% or more in the 10th or 12th examination: ₹25,000/- per year.\n- On securing 70% to 79.99% in the 10th or 12th examination: ₹15,000/- per year.\n- On securing 60% to 69.99% in the 10th or 12th examination: ₹10,000/- per year.\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "\"Cash Prizes Scheme\" was launched by the Bihar Building & Other Construction Workers Welfare Board. Students securing 60% or more in the 10th and 12th exams receive cash prizes of up to ₹25,000/- per year. Upto two children of a registered construction worker are eligible.",
